definition: to stick up/to rise on one end/to tilt

sentences.english: Bedrock beneath hebgen lake warped and rotated, causing a seiche in the lake .
sentences.chinese: 赫布根湖底的基岩发生了翘曲和旋转，引起湖中浪涌。

sentences.english: It has improved impact resistance and low warpage.
sentences.chinese: 它改善了耐冲击性和低翘曲。

sentences.english: All the window frames of the old building have sprung.
sentences.chinese: 这幢旧楼的所有窗框全都翘曲了。

sentences.english: The floor of the house has been started.
sentences.chinese: 那所房间里的地板都已翘曲了。

sentences.english: The values of warping coordinates is still expressed in the calculating formulas.
sentences.chinese: 翘曲座标值，仍以计算公式表示之。

sentences.english: Thickening the wall will help reduce orientation related warpage problems.
sentences.chinese: 增加壁厚将有助于减少因取向引起的翘曲问题。

sentences.english: It is a funny and easy to use application for photo morphing and warping.
sentences.chinese: 这是一个有趣且易于使用的应用为照片变形和翘曲。

sentences.english: Next, inspect the gusset for warpage and straighten as needed.
sentences.chinese: 下一步，检查和整顿的翘曲扣板根据需要的一面。

sentences.english: According to the statistical results, the injection time is the most important affecting factor on warpage.
sentences.chinese: 结果表明，注射时间对注塑件翘曲变形的影响最大。

sentences.english: Thicker parts also tend to warp less.
sentences.chinese: 较厚零件也有助于减少翘曲。

sentences.english: The speckle projection correlation technique is used to measure the chip warpage.
sentences.chinese: 本文采用投影散斑相关法对芯片翘曲度进行了测量。

sentences.english: So what do you do when your profile warps?
sentences.chinese: 那么，型材翘曲时，我们该怎样做呢？

sentences.english: The warped phenomenon is mitigated when the chordal height decreases.
sentences.chinese: 随着弦高的减小，翘曲现象减轻，渐呈准直线。
